race.description: Qx3 Sports Michael Shanahan Maiden Plate
race.comment: BAZZAR (5) found one too good on debut but made an impression. Resumes today and has been good at the jumpouts. Has a handy gate and will be naturally improved. DIRNASEER (8) sat just off the speed and fought on well when just beaten first-up at this course/ distance. Has a wide gate to contend with, but Egan goes on and has trialled him. Needs some luck but is ready to salute. BUZITUP (1) settled well back from a wide draw but wound up strongly when just missing this track and trip. Draws wide again but will be fitter and will be winding up strongly. BUNDORAN (10) looked a run short first-up and will be sharper today. Has more to give and has each way claims. BURLEIGH (6) is an improver from the premier stable, but the 3kg claimer will need a special from the outside barrier.
